## Review Decision Matrix

| Category | Pass | Modify | Block |
|----------|------|--------|-------|
| State management | Secure, locked, recoverable | Minor gaps | State in VCS, no locking |
| Drift detection | Automated, in CI | Partial | No drift detection |
| Cost controls | Estimated, tagged, alerts | Gaps documented | Unbounded cost risk |
| Module design | Clean, versioned | Refactor needed | Monolithic, unsafe |
| Environment separation | Isolated, approved | Minor gaps | Shared prod creds |
| Secrets | External only | Some inline | Secrets in code |
| Naming/tagging | Consistent, enforced | Partial | No tagging |

